{
  "stem": "19923.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And arrangements were made to take the whole group into the chateau eventually because that would be perhaps the best place to hide from the prying eyes of the French police and the Germans.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And six months before I came to United States in-- sometime in the winter of 1940-41, probably early 1941, we all boarded trucks and we went south to Chateau le Hille.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And the people-- the advance group that went there, the older boys and older girls, had gone there and put in the electricity.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And we didn't have any toilets, so they put electricity and water.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And for toilets, they dug a big hole at the back of the chateau, put wooden boards around it, and that became our toilet-- just a big hole with boards over it-- until they eventually were able to get plumbing in and get toilets.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "But for a few months, that's all we had.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And when we went there--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We went there from Seyre by trucks.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We hired-- somewhere, we got a hold of some trucks and we went south.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And all of us came to Chateau le Hille.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And from there is where I came to the United States.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The chateau-- we were completely unknown.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We-- the older people would go to the next village and work if they could.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We planted our own food, we had our own garden.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were pretty well self-sufficient.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it was really operated almost like a farm.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We would have-- we would go and get goat's milk from the neighbors.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I think we had-- we had-- I think we had some goats that we were able to get for the young children.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we had the life of a kibbutz.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was completely self-sufficient.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
